            - vast_search, vast_rent, vast_connect, vast_broadcast, vast_distribute
            ... and 80+ more. Use get_status() to see current state.
            \"\"\"
            if isinstance(args, dict):
                parsed_args = dict(args)
            else:
                try:
                    parsed_args = json.loads(args) if args else {{}}
                except Exception:
